Method: set_global_start_position(position: Vector2) → void
Sets the global position of the link's start point.
Method: set_navigation_layer_value(layer_number: int, value: bool) → void
Sets or unsets the navigation layer bitmask for the given layer number.
Method: set_navigation_map(navigation_map: RID) → void
Sets the NavigationMap for this link to use.
